Name: Feedback
Review_Description__c:
Hello everyone, I generally don''t write review. But, I will write for this one because I have heard many negative feedback about flipkart on Quora and I was in doubt whether to purchase it from Flipkart or not.
Lets talk about Flipkart first.
Delivery was on time and It was free. 
Installation was also free however you have to pay for stands (750 Rupees in my case) . Voltage regulator is optional.
So, overall I am happy with the service of flipkart.
Now, coming to AC
It's around 1000 watt machine works on Single Phase power supply  which do produce humming sound (which is quite normal). Cooling is pretty good and fast. I have been using this product for last 10 days and I have not found any issue with cooling.
Overall this product is good..

Go for it..

Name: Pretty good
Review_Description__c:
Product is good  but while Flipkart after discount price is shown as 27,500/-, the MRP printed on packing box is 23,500/-! So is it a genuine discount or a rip off?  Better check the price directly with Blue Star office before buying. Also the unit which was deliverd to me carried a manufacturing date more than a year old. If its lying in stock for more than a year, what's wrong with it? Maybe a longer period usage will tell me. 
The installation is free as per Flipkart. But when fitting men come, they first insist it is not free. After lot of arguments and them acting as if they are cheking with their office, they agree it is free but after installation, will claim substantial amount as extra charge for white tape or rubber base bushing or something like that. I had to pay finally Rs 600/- as didnt want to continue the fight. So before installation , make everything clear that there should be no charge asked after installation.

Review_Description__c: Voltas - Damn good AC for the 10x10 room , it gets cold in the night so we have to switch it off , trick is to place it above the bed so in peak summer it blows  cool air directly where u sit , otherwise u will have to wait for room to get cold . R32 inverter / silent and good design , easy to install and no hassle long cables with padding which shows quality , all my other ac had cheap padding on external cables , outside is quiet and inside sound  is less than normal fan , modes are same , fan , cool and dry i think , i use cool so not much there and turbo or chill mode that's all. I had voltas earlier water dispenser and it lasted long so hope same here , price is very cheap compared to local stores and it came in 2 days for small city it is good.  Take care of yearly cleaning of ac u will do well.  Split and inverter is way to go , it consumes 1 unit per hr , i would assume i will use some 500 - 770 units in summer for year.

Voltas AC overall very nice. Before I had Samsung AC, now Voltas. From cooling and other aspects it is very nice. Till now it's running very well. Flipkart delivery was excellent too and guys were very nice with their attitude.

But what forced me to put 4 star instead of 5 is very poor Installation process. The guy called me from Jeeves service and were asking to pay around Rs. 2000-2500 to set this machine as they just need to remove my old machine and install new one. He was Bargaining with me so I cancelled it and installed it with my local electrician who took just half of that price. 

Conclusion, AC is good but Installation experience so worst.

Name: Just wow!
Review_Description__c: When it comes to Airconditioner, nothing beats the king of India, our beloved Voltas. Have been using it from more than a decade and hence decided to get one more, as expected it is as good as it was earlier if not better. Good performance in the scorching heat and humidity. After sales is also being a string point to consider this as an option. Easy to service and parts are also affordable.

Name: Just wow! and Excellent Installation by Voltas
Review_Description__c: Good Product, Sturdy plastic and installation was excellent by Voltas. Cooling is also excellent than I expected. I have 10 * 12 room with fully furnished cupboards. During night, turbo mode is effective and cools the room in 10 mins. Got this one for INR 30,500 with R32 gas. Its worth for the money I paid.

Name: Super!
